在代数学中，'''胡尔维兹定理'''（又名“1,2,4,8定理”）是以在1898年证明它的[[阿道夫·胡尔维兹|阿道夫·胡尔维兹]]命名。该定理表明：任何带有单位元的[[賦範可除代數|賦範可除代數]]同构于以下四个代数之一：R,C,H和O，分别代表[[实数|实数]]、[[复数_(数学)|复数]]、[[四元数|四元数]]和[[八元数|八元数]]。<ref name=Nieto>

{{cite journal |title=Hurwitz theorem and parallelizable spheres from tensor analysis |author=JA Nieto and LN Alejo-Armenta |year=2000 |url=http://arxiv.org/abs/hep-th/0005184v2 |journal=Arxiv preprint hep-th/0005184}}

</ref><ref name=McCrimmon>

{{cite book |title=A taste of Jordan algebras |author= Kevin McCrimmon |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=6YG4ycpKMYkC&pg=PA166 |page=166 |chapter=Hurwitz's theorem 2.6.2 |quote=Only recently was it established that the only ''finite-dimensional'' real nonassociative division algebras have dimensions 1,2,4,8; the algebras were not classified, and the proof was topological rather than algebraic.|isbn=0387954473 |year=2004 |publisher=Springer}} 

</ref>对实賦範可除代數的分类始于弗洛比纽斯<ref name=Frobenius>

{{cite journal |author=Georg Frobenius |title= Über lineare Substitutionen und blineare Formen |journal=J. Reine Angew. Math. |volume=84 |pages=1–63 |year=1878}}

</ref> ，发扬于胡尔维兹<ref name=Hurwitz>

